    "Name": "Bandit PRIME",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Bandit Hovercraft Prime</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Standard </color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>9/14 (Hover)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>215 Fusion</color></b>\n\nThe Bandit is a 50-ton combat hovercraft originally designed by the Clans. Brought to the Inner Sphere by the Wolf's Dragoons, it was produced by Blackwell Corporation in 3007 for their exclusive use.\n\nThe Bandit's primary configuration carries three Medium Lasers in its turret, along with two front-mounted SRM-2 launchers and a Machine Gun. Ammunition includes two tons of SRM-2 reloads, along with one-half ton for the Machine Gun.",
